{"tid":2267631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人堅決唔會投委任派？","createTime":"2020-11-02T08:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:40:45.000Z","uid":134103,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd501fa6b733654081c95a38b45296eeba0d092","tid":2267631,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:08:00.000Z","msg":"委任派今次真係令人太失望，係都要留喺個垃圾議會入面，我又唔明佢班友除咗幫對家營造一個「議會入面有反對聲音嘅議會」之外仲有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將來再有選舉，我真係投唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然冇可能投對家，如果剩係得委任派同對家俾我揀，我會選擇唔投<br />\n<br />\n預咗俾人屌分化/五毛，不過都想聽下大家意見，睇下有冇人同我一樣諗法，或者講到俾我知應該點投"},{"pid":"6de8a9baf76d5f924c3a5fb9bc44394e7a6b8128","tid":2267631,"uid":61914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"我都唔會投<br />\n唔係分唔分化既問題，而係呢班人基本上無哂credibility"},{"pid":"fc538e37b73fd1c4f7ce053f778fcb7fbb9b0f1c","tid":2267631,"uid":210382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"你不如諗其他好過啦，你覺得仲有下次選舉。大灣區過左你投咩都係選唔到"},{"pid":"1aed2edad73bc58c1f44aa9a8928c0778a7be052","tid":2267631,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:09:27.000Z","msg":"投唔投都罷啦<br />\n<br />\n你投票即係話呢個議會仲有認受性<br />\n<br />\n唔係橡皮圖章"},{"pid":"a1ee60c8b325289a68c35c8731dd5cff2caa94d3","tid":2267631,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc538e37b73fd1c4f7ce053f778fcb7fbb9b0f1c","tid":2267631,"uid":210382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"你不如諗其他好過啦，你覺得仲有下次選舉。大灣區過左你投咩都係選唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"咁點都會留返十席八席比啲委任派做下樣嘅<br />\n<br />\n澳門都有兩個飯民啦"},{"pid":"d6a160a0fb6686223a49928b42b38208564751f2","tid":2267631,"uid":50931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de8a9baf76d5f924c3a5fb9bc44394e7a6b8128","tid":2267631,"uid":61914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTi